### Introduction to Equity > What can teachers do?

#### What can teachers do?
Code.org is committed to helping all educators create equitable computer science learning environments. All of [our professional development offerings](https://code.org/educate/professional-development) include opportunities for teachers to consider their own biases and assumptions, to discuss the implications of inequity in CS, and to explore strategies for creating equity in classrooms.
